==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: biosynthesis
<hw>biosynthesis</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>production of a
chemical compound by a living organism.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> biogenesis.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the production of chemical substances by use of
reagents or enzymes derived from living organisms, in reactions modeled
on those observed in living organisms.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>biosynthetic</ent>⟦br⟧
